OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774803956
OL,3,CFour teens charged in connection with
OL,4,CBangor attack
OL,6,FFour youths have been charged over an
OL,7,Fincident in which a man and dog were
OL,8,Fassaulted in Co Down on Friday.
OL,10,FA charity said one of its volunteers
OL,11,Fwas attacked and the animal targeted
OL,12,Fwas a search and rescue dog.
OL,14,FDetectives received a report at around
OL,15,F7.50pm on Friday night of an ongoing
OL,16,Ffight involving a number of youths and
OL,17,Fa man in the High Street area of
OL,18,FBangor.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
