OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774803956
OL,3,CFour teens charged in connection with
OL,4,CBangor attack
OL,6,FUpon arrival at the scene, officers
OL,7,Fsaw a number of young people running
OL,8,Foff, most of them dressed in dark
OL,9,Fclothing.
OL,11,FIt was reported that the man was
OL,12,Fpunched to the face multiple times by
OL,13,Fa number of the youths and his dog was
OL,14,Fkicked a number of times.
OL,16,FProviding an update, the PSNI said a
OL,17,F13-year-old boy has been charged with
OL,18,Fassault occasioning actual bodily
OL,19,Fharm, affray and causing unnecessary
OL,20,Fsuffering to an animal.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
