OL,3,CFour teens charged in connection with
OL,4,CBangor attack
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fwith assault occasioning actual bodily
OL,8,Fharm, affray and causing unnecessary
OL,9,Fsuffering to an animal, while another
OL,10,F15-year-old boy has been charged with
OL,11,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm
OL,12,Fand affray.
OL,14,FA 16-year-old girl has been charged
OL,15,Fwith affray and common assault.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
