OL,3,CFour teens charged in connection with
OL,4,CBangor attack
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Police
OL,7,Fwould like to thank all those members
OL,8,Fof the public who came forward to
OL,9,Fassist with inquiries following our
OL,10,Fappeal for information in relation to
OL,11,Fthis incident.
OL,13,F"The investigation is ongoing and
OL,14,Ffurther arrests will be made when the
OL,15,Fother suspects are identified."
